posting_body: ['The Retreat at Fox Hollow Apartments boasts beautiful lush landscapes that offer unencumbered views of stunning natural surroundings.', 'Wake up to breathtaking views of the nearby mountains and enjoy an eclectic neighborhood with a dynamic feel.', 'Calling the Retreat at Fox Hollow “home” is easy when you step into your luxurious apartment, complete with a private balcony, fireplace, alarm system, and even your in-home washer and dryer.', 'Life can be truly comfortable when you consider the vast array of amenities that will be right at your fingertips at The Retreat at Fox Hollow.', '-Private Patio/Balcony', '-Year Round Hot Tub', '-Dog Washing Station', '-Outdoor Firepit and Barbecue Grills', '-Dishwasher, Microwave', '-9 Foot Ceilings with Crown Molding', '-Built-in Desks / Book Shelves', '-All', 'Buildings 2 Stories', '-Spectacular Clubhouse', '-Rocky Mountain Views', '-Emergency Maintenance', '-Ceiling fans', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Our pricing changes daily.', 'Please call or email us today for updated pricing and availability.']
